STATE of North Carolina
v.
George Franklin PAGE. No. 239A96-5. Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 1, 2005. Walter L. Jones, Greensboro, Amiel J. Rossabi, for George Franklin Page. Valerie B. Spalding, Special Deputy Attorney General, Thomas J. Keith, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 12th day of August 2005 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Forsyth County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 1st day of December 2005."
